-- Diamond-Crafted IPhone Offered in Moscow Gift Store, RBC Says
-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 2012-04-06T08:44:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-06/diamond-crafted-iphone-offered-in-moscow-gift-store-rbc-says.html
Bon Cadeau, a luxury gift store in
Moscow, is selling a variant of  Apple Inc. (AAPL) ’s iPhone customized
set with diamonds for $12,000,  RBC  said.  The smartphone’s body, designed by Sun & Moon, is made of
18-karat gold with 850 encrusted diamonds, including a pink
diamond that replaces the home button, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow at 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
